  "texts": [
    "Further details regarding the articles can be found in the Methods section and in ref. 32.",
    "Specifically focusing on polymer-related content, we identified 681,000 documents by searching for the term 'poly' in the title and abstract of the articles.",
    "Extracting information from these polymer-related documents involved treating individual paragraphs as text units, resulting in a total of 23.3 million paragraphs.",
    "To extract data from the selected paragraphs, we targeted 24 properties of polymers based on their significance and downstream usage.",
    "Commonly reported thermal and optical properties were selected for their efficacy in training multi-task ML models, using highly correlated properties as substitutes for less prevalent ones."
  ],
